<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>otimismo.pt — Notícias Positivas para um Mundo Melhor</title>
<meta name="description" content="As melhores notícias positivas de Portugal e do mundo. Informação que inspira, histórias que transformam.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
:root {
  --blue-50:#EEF6FD; --blue-100:#C8E4F7; --blue-200:#87C4EE;
  --blue-300:#4BA3D9; --blue-400:#2B7DB5; --blue-500:#1A5F8A;
  --navy:#1A2B3C; --navy-soft:#2D3F50;
  --gray-100:#F5F7FA; --gray-200:#E8ECF1; --gray-400:#9BA8B5; --gray-600:#5C6B7A;
  --white:#FFFFFF; --green-soft:#E8F5EE; --green-mid:#2E9E6B;
  --gold:#F59E0B; --gold-light:#FEF3C7;
  --radius-sm:6px; --radius-md:12px; --radius-lg:20px;
  --font-serif:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;
  --font-sans:'DM Sans',system-ui,sans-serif;
  --shadow-sm:0 1px 3px rgba(27,43,60,.08);
  --shadow-md:0 4px 16px rgba(27,43,60,.10);
  --shadow-hover:0 8px 32px rgba(27,43,60,.14);
}
html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
body { font-family:var(--font-sans); background:var(--gray-100); color:var(--navy); font-size:16px; line-height:1.65; }

/* ── TOPBAR ── */
.topbar { background:var(--blue-400); color:var(--blue-50); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.06em; text-align:center; padding:7px 16px; font-weight:500; }
.topbar strong { color:#fff; }

/* ── HEADER ── */
header { background:var(--white); border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200); position:sticky; top:0; z-index:100; box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm); }
.header-inner { max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; height:68px; gap:20px; }
.logo-link { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; text-decoration:none; flex-shrink:0; }
.logo-img { width:44px; height:44px; object-fit:contain; }
.logo-text { display:flex; flex-direction:column; line-height:1; }
.logo-name { font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:20px; font-weight:500; color:var(--navy); letter-spacing:-.02em; }
.logo-name span { color:var(--blue-300); }
.logo-tagline { font-size:10px; letter-spacing:.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blue-300); font-weight:500; margin-top:2px; }

.main-nav { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; }
.main-nav a { font-size:14px; font-weight:500; color:var(--gray-600); padding:6px 14px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); text-decoration:none; transition:all .2s; white-space:nowrap; }
.main-nav a:hover { background:var(--blue-50); color:var(--blue-400); }
.main-nav a.active { background:var(--blue-50); color:var(--blue-400); font-weight:600; }

.header-actions { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; flex-shrink:0; }
.btn-newsletter { background:var(--blue-400); color:#fff; border:none; padding:9px 18px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-size:14px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; transition:background .2s; font-family:var(--font-sans); text-decoration:none; white-space:nowrap; }
.btn-newsletter:hover { background:var(--blue-500); }
.btn-apoiar { background:var(--gold); color:#fff; border:none; padding:9px 14px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-size:13px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; transition:background .2s; font-family:var(--font-sans); text-decoration:none; white-space:nowrap; }
.btn-apoiar:hover { background:#d97706; }

.hamburger { display:none; background:none; border:none; cursor:pointer; padding:6px; }
.hamburger span { display:block; width:22px; height:2px; background:var(--navy); margin:5px 0; border-radius:2px; transition:.2s; }

/* ── MOBILE MENU ── */
.mobile-menu { display:none; background:var(--white); border-top:1px solid var(--gray-200); padding:12px 24px 16px; }
.mobile-menu a { display:block; padding:10px 0; font-size:15px; font-weight:500; color:var(--navy); text-decoration:none; border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200); }
.mobile-menu a:last-child { border-bottom:none; }

/* ── CATEGORY TABS ── */
.cat-bar { background:var(--white); border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200); position:sticky; top:68px; z-index:90; }
.cat-bar-inner { max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px; display:flex; gap:0; overflow-x:auto; scrollbar-width:none; }
.cat-bar-inner::-webkit-scrollbar { display:none; }
.cat-tab { font-size:13px; font-weight:500; padding:12px 16px; color:var(--gray-600); border-bottom:2px solid transparent; white-space:nowrap; cursor:pointer; transition:all .2s; background:none; border-left:none; border-right:none; border-top:none; font-family:var(--font-sans); }
.cat-tab:hover { color:var(--blue-400); }
.cat-tab.active { color:var(--blue-400); border-bottom-color:var(--blue-400); font-weight:600; }

/* ── HERO ── */
.hero { background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--blue-50) 0%,#dbeeff 60%,var(--blue-100) 100%); padding:48px 24px 52px; }
.hero-inner { max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; display:flex; gap:40px; align-items:center; }
.hero-text { flex:1; }
.hero-label { font-size:11px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blue-400); margin-bottom:12px; }
.hero h1 { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.8rem); font-weight:700; color:var(--navy); line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:14px; }
.hero h1 em { font-style:normal; color:var(--blue-400); }
.hero p { font-size:16px; color:var(--gray-600); line-height:1.7; max-width:480px; }
.hero-stats { display:flex; gap:24px; margin-top:24px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.hero-stat { text-align:center; }
.hero-stat strong { display:block; font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.8rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--blue-400); }
.hero-stat span { font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em; color:var(--gray-600); }

/* ── AD BANNER ── */
.ad-banner { background:var(--white); border:1px dashed var(--gray-200); border-radius:var(--radius-md); padding:16px; text-align:center; color:var(--gray-400); font-size:12px; letter-spacing:.04em; text-transform:uppercase; }
.ad-banner-top { max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:12px 24px; }
.ad-slot { background:var(--white); border:1px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius:var(--radius-md); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:var(--gray-400); font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em; }

/* ── TICKER ── */
.ticker-wrap { background:var(--blue-400); overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0; }
.ticker-inner { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; padding:0 16px; }
.ticker-badge { flex-shrink:0; background:rgba(255,255,255,.2); color:#fff; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:20px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; }
.ticker-scroll-wrap { overflow:hidden; flex:1; }
@keyframes scroll { 0%{transform:translateX(0)} 100%{transform:translateX(-50%)} }
.ticker-text { display:inline-block; white-space:nowrap; color:#fff; font-size:13px; font-weight:500; animation:scroll 40s linear infinite; }
.ticker-text:hover { animation-play-state:paused; }

/* ── MAIN LAYOUT ── */
.main-wrap { max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:28px 24px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 300px; gap:28px; }
@media(max-width:900px){ .main-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr} .sidebar{display:none} }

/* ── FEATURED NEWS ── */
.featured-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.6fr 1fr; gap:16px; margin-bottom:28px; }
@media(max-width:700px){ .featured-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr} }
.featured-main { background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--navy) 0%,var(--blue-500) 100%); border-radius:var(--radius-lg); overflow:hidden; padding:28px; color:#fff; position:relative; min-height:260px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:flex-end; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none; }
.featured-main:hover .feat-title { color:var(--blue-100); }
.feat-badge { display:inline-block; background:var(--blue-300); color:#fff; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:20px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; margin-bottom:10px; }
.feat-title { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.35rem; font-weight:700; line-height:1.3; color:#fff; margin-bottom:10px; transition:color .2s; }
.feat-meta { font-size:12px; color:var(--blue-100); display:flex; gap:10px; }
.feat-score { background:rgba(255,255,255,.15); padding:2px 8px; border-radius:12px; }

.featured-side { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; }
.feat-card-sm { background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-md); overflow:hidden; display:flex; gap:12px; padding:14px; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none; transition:box-shadow .2s,transform .2s; border:1px solid var(--gray-200); }
.feat-card-sm:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow-hover); transform:translateY(-2px); }
.feat-card-sm .thumb { width:64px; height:64px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); object-fit:cover; flex-shrink:0; background:var(--blue-100); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:1.4rem; }
.feat-card-sm .info { flex:1; min-width:0; }
.feat-card-sm .cat-tag { font-size:9px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; color:var(--blue-400); margin-bottom:4px; }
.feat-card-sm .title-sm { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:.85rem; font-weight:600; line-height:1.35; color:var(--navy); display:-webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp:2; -webkit-box-orient:vertical; overflow:hidden; }
.feat-card-sm .source-sm { font-size:11px; color:var(--gray-400); margin-top:4px; }

/* ── NEWS SECTION HEADER ── */
.section-header { display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:16px; }
.section-title { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--navy); }
.section-link { font-size:13px; color:var(--blue-400); text-decoration:none; font-weight:500; }
.section-link:hover { text-decoration:underline; }

/* ── NEWS GRID ── */
.news-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(260px,1fr)); gap:16px; }
@keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)} to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)} }
.news-card { background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-md); overflow:hidden; border:1px solid var(--gray-200); transition:box-shadow .2s,transform .2s; display:flex; flex-direction:column; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none; animation:fadeUp .35s ease both; }
.news-card:hover { box-shadow:var(--shadow-hover); transform:translateY(-3px); }
.news-card .thumb { width:100%; height:165px; object-fit:cover; background:var(--blue-100); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:2rem; }
.news-card .body { padding:14px; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; }
.cat-pill { display:inline-block; font-size:9px; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.09em; padding:3px 8px; border-radius:20px; background:var(--blue-50); color:var(--blue-400); margin-bottom:8px; }
.cat-pill.desporto { background:#fff3e0; color:#e65100; }
.cat-pill.saude { background:#fce4ec; color:#c2185b; }
.cat-pill.ambiente { background:#e8f5e9; color:#2e7d32; }
.cat-pill.economia { background:#f3e5f5; color:#6a1b9a; }
.cat-pill.tecnologia { background:#e3f2fd; color:#1565c0; }
.cat-pill.sociedade { background:#e8eaf6; color:#283593; }
.cat-pill.ciencia { background:#e0f7fa; color:#00695c; }
.card-title { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:.95rem; font-weight:700; line-height:1.4; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:8px; display:-webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp:3; -webkit-box-orient:vertical; overflow:hidden; }
.card-summary { font-size:.82rem; color:var(--gray-600); line-height:1.55; flex:1; display:-webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp:3; -webkit-box-orient:vertical; overflow:hidden; }
.card-footer { margin-top:12px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; font-size:.75rem; }
.card-source { color:var(--gray-400); }
.card-score { display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; color:var(--green-mid); font-weight:600; }
.score-dots { display:flex; gap:2px; }
.score-dot { width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--gray-200); }
.score-dot.filled { background:var(--green-mid); }

@keyframes shimmer { 0%{background-position:-600px 0} 100%{background-position:600px 0} }
.skel { border-radius:var(--radius-md); background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gray-200) 25%,var(--gray-100) 50%,var(--gray-200) 75%); background-size:1200px 100%; animation:shimmer 1.4s infinite; }
.skel-card { height:280px; }

.load-more-wrap { text-align:center; margin-top:24px; }
.btn-load-more { background:var(--white); color:var(--blue-400); border:1.5px solid var(--blue-200); padding:11px 28px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-size:14px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; transition:all .2s; font-family:var(--font-sans); }
.btn-load-more:hover { background:var(--blue-50); border-color:var(--blue-300); }

/* ── SIDEBAR ── */
.sidebar { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:20px; }
.sidebar-card { background:var(--white); border-radius:var(--radius-md); border:1px solid var(--gray-200); overflow:hidden; }
.sidebar-card-header { padding:14px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200); font-family:var(--font-serif); font-weight:700; font-size:1rem; color:var(--navy); }
.sidebar-card-body { padding:16px; }

/* Apoiar card */
.apoiar-card { background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold-light),#fde68a); border-radius:var(--radius-md); padding:18px; text-align:center; border:1px solid #fcd34d; }
.apoiar-icon { font-size:2rem; margin-bottom:8px; }
.apoiar-title { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-weight:700; color:var(--navy); font-size:1rem; margin-bottom:6px; }
.apoiar-desc { font-size:.8rem; color:var(--gray-600); line-height:1.5; margin-bottom:12px; }
.apoiar-amounts { display:flex; gap:6px; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:12px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.amount-btn { background:#fff; border:1.5px solid var(--gold); color:#92400e; font-weight:700; font-size:13px; padding:6px 14px; border-radius:20px; cursor:pointer; transition:all .2s; font-family:var(--font-sans); }
.amount-btn:hover, .amount-btn.active { background:var(--gold); color:#fff; }
.btn-apoiar-main { width:100%; background:var(--gold); color:#fff; border:none; padding:11px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-size:14px; font-weight:700; cursor:pointer; transition:background .2s; font-family:var(--font-sans); }
.btn-apoiar-main:hover { background:#d97706; }

/* Newsletter sidebar */
.newsletter-form input { width:100%; padding:9px 12px; border:1.5px solid var(--gray-200); border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-size:13px; font-family:var(--font-sans); margin-bottom:8px; }
.newsletter-form input:focus { outline:none; border-color:var(--blue-300); }
.btn-subscribe { width:100%; background:var(--blue-400); color:#fff; border:none; padding:10px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); font-size:13px; font-weight:600; cursor:pointer; font-family:var(--font-sans); transition:background .2s; }
.btn-subscribe:hover { background:var(--blue-500); }

/* Trending */
.trending-item { display:flex; gap:10px; padding:10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--gray-200); cursor:pointer; text-decoration:none; }
.trending-item:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.trending-num { font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--blue-100); flex-shrink:0; width:28px; line-height:1; }
.trending-title { font-size:.82rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); line-height:1.35; }
.trending-cat { font-size:.72rem; color:var(--gray-400); margin-top:2px; }

/* Ad sidebar */
.ad-sidebar { background:var(--gray-100); border:1px dashed var(--gray-200); border-radius:var(--radius-md); height:250px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; text-align:center; color:var(--gray-400); font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em; }

/* Partilhar */
.share-row { display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.share-btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:5px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; padding:7px 12px; border-radius:var(--radius-sm); text-decoration:none; transition:opacity .2s; }
.share-btn:hover { opacity:.82; }

/* ── FOOTER ── */
footer { background:var(--navy); color:#8DA4B8; margin-top:48px; }
.footer-inner { max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; padding:40px 24px; display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap:32px; }
@media(max-width:700px){ .footer-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr} }
.footer-brand { font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:500; color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px; }
.footer-brand span { color:var(--blue-300); }
.footer-desc { font-size:.85rem; line-height:1.6; }
.footer-col h4 { color:#fff; font-size:.85rem; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:12px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.06em; }
.footer-col a { display:block; font-size:.85rem; color:#8DA4B8; text-decoration:none; margin-bottom:6px; transition:color .2s; }
.footer-col a:hover { color:#fff; }
.footer-bottom { border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); padding:16px 24px; text-align:center; font-size:.78rem; color:#5C7A96; max-width:1200px; margin:0 auto; }

/* ── TOAST ── */
.toast { position:fixed; bottom:20px; right:20px; background:var(--navy); color:#fff; padding:12px 20px; border-radius:var(--radius-md); font-size:.875rem; font-weight:500; z-index:9999; opacity:0; transform:translateY(12px); transition:all .3s; box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.25); max-width:300px; }
.toast.show { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media(max-width:768px){
  .main-nav { display:none; }
  .header-actions .btn-apoiar { display:none; }
  .hamburger { display:block; }
  .hero-inner { flex-direction:column; }
  .hero h1 { font-size:1.6rem; }
  .featured-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="topbar">
  <strong>✦ otimismo.pt</strong> <span>— Notícias com impacto positivo, renovadas diariamente</span><span id="lastUpdate" style="margin-left:10px;opacity:.75;font-size:11px;"></span>
</div>

<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <a href="#" class="logo-link">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64, " class="logo-img">
      <div class="logo-text">
        <span class="logo-name">otimismo<span>.pt</span></span>
        <span class="logo-tagline">Jornalismo de Soluções</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    <nav class="main-nav">
      <a href="#" class="active">Início</a>
      <a href="#">Sobre Nós</a>
      <a href="#">Impacto</a>
      <a href="#">Contacto</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="header-actions">
      <a href="#" class="btn-apoiar">Apoiar Projeto</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-newsletter">Newsletter</a>
      <button class="hamburger" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Menu">
        <span></span><span></span><span></span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
  <a href="#">Início</a>
  <a href="#">Sobre Nós</a>
  <a href="#">Impacto</a>
  <a href="#">Contacto</a>
  <a href="#" style="color:var(--gold)">Apoiar Projeto</a>
</div>

<div class="cat-bar">
  <div class="cat-bar-inner" id="catTabs">
    <button class="cat-tab active" data-cat="todas">Todas</button>
    <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="ambiente">Ambiente</button>
    <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="saude">Saúde</button>
    <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="tecnologia">Tecnologia</button>
    <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="economia">Economia</button>
    <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="ciencia">Ciência</button>
    <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="sociedade">Sociedade</button>
    <button class="cat-tab" data-cat="desporto">Desporto</button>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-label">Jornalismo Independente</div>
      <h1>As boas notícias que <br><em>transformam</em> o mundo.</h1>
      <p>Acompanha histórias de progresso, inovação e solidariedade em Portugal e no mundo. Informação rigorosa, focada nas soluções.</p>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="hero-stat"><strong>+15k</strong><span>Leitores Diários</span></div>
        <div class="hero-stat"><strong>100%</strong><span>Livre de Ruído</span></div>
        <div class="hero-stat"><strong>20+</strong><span>Fontes Globais</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ad-banner-top" style="flex:1; max-width:420px;">
      <div class="ad-slot" style="height:180px;">Publicidade / Apoio institucional</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="ticker-wrap">
  <div class="ticker-inner">
    <span class="ticker-badge">Última hora positiva</span>
    <div class="ticker-scroll-wrap">
      <div class="ticker-text" id="tickerText">A carregar os mais recentes avanços globais...</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="main-wrap">
  
  <main>
    <div class="featured-grid" id="featuredSection">
      </div>

    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-title" id="gridTitle">Feed de Notícias Inspiradoras</div>
    </div>

    <div class="news-grid" id="newsGrid">
      <div class="skel skel-card"></div>
      <div class="skel skel-card"></div>
      <div class="skel skel-card"></div>
      <div class="skel skel-card"></div>
      <div class="skel skel-card"></div>
      <div class="skel skel-card"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="load-more-wrap">
      <button class="btn-load-more" id="btnLoadMore">Ver Mais Notícias</button>
    </div>
  </main>

  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="apoiar-card">
      <div class="apoiar-icon">🌱</div>
      <h3 class="apoiar-title">Ajuda o Otimismo a Crescer</h3>
      <p class="apoiar-desc">Somos um projeto independente. O teu apoio direto garante jornalismo sem sensacionalismo e focado no futuro.</p>
      <div class="apoiar-amounts">
        <button class="amount-btn">2€</button>
        <button class="amount-btn active">5€</button>
        <button class="amount-btn">10€</button>
